# DS Platform User Guide

Welcome to the Data Science Platform! 

This platform provides a standardized, reproducible, and scalable environment for data science projects. It integrates **JupyterHub** (workspaces), **Forgejo** (Git version control), and **Grafana** (monitoring) into a cohesive workflow.

