## 5. Monitoring & Observability

Access Grafana at [https://monitoring.{{ parent_domain }}](https://monitoring.{{ parent_domain }}).

### 5.1 Dashboards
* **Provisioned Dashboards:** You will see ready-made dashboards.
    * *Note:* These dashboards are **Read-Only** (provisioned as code). If you need to edit one, open it, click "Settings" (gear icon), and **Save As...** a new JSON file to create your own editable copy.

### 5.2 Logs
* **Loki:** Use the **Drilldown** tab in Grafana. Select **Logs**.

### 5.3 Alerts
* **Grafana Alerting:** The platform monitors for high resource usage. If the host machine exceeds **85% CPU or Memory**, an alert is sent to the **MS Teams** chat. If you see a notification, please check whether your running processes aren't hanging or optimizing poorly.

